dct_description_sm: Map of a U.S. Department of the Interior Geological Survey of the Pleasantville Quadrangle in Atlantic County, N.J. This sheet includes two insets for an index of boundaries and a depiction of Pleasantville and surrounding quadrangles. Extensive legend showing types of topography.
Stamped as a Drury University College U.S. Depository copy along with a date Jul. 28, 1949.
